<h2 id="insert-a-layout">Insert a Layout</h2>

<p>Add a layout to your map.  Choose the 8.5‚Äù:‚Äù x 11‚Äù Letter size, in the Landscape orientation.  Your task is to create a layout with <strong>one map</strong> and <strong>two charts</strong>.  The map should show the Housing Cost by Census Tract and the charts should show Housing cost vs. Mean NDVI and Percent Green Space respectively.</p>

<h2 id="tidying-things-up-and-adding-items-to-the-layout">Tidying Things Up and Adding Items to the Layout</h2>

<p>This video gives a few tips for how you can clean up your data before making your map so its a bit more presentatble.</p>

<h1 id="adding-a-chart-to-the-layout">Adding a Chart to the Layout</h1>

<p>Arc allows you to add charts to your layout in addition to maps.</p>

